Cassandra


keyspace - database


To Create Keyspace

CREATE KEYSPACE demo WITH replication = {'class' : 'SimpleStrategy', 'replication_factor' : 3};

use demo;

CREATE TABLE godatafy (name varchar PRIMARY KEY);

select * from godatafy;

insert into godatafy (name) values ('Ariv');


exit

data file direcoties.

To take backup

nodetool snapshot demo

drop KEYSPACE demo

To recover

sudo apt install tree - To view 

nodetool refresh demo godatafy - to recover
